{"tid":2062825,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：不排除武漢肺炎病毒經空氣而非飛沬傳播","createTime":"2020-06-13T12:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:01:39.000Z","uid":348984,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4bd59cd2bad17f82badbb151c1fe59386811f5","tid":2062825,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓再多一人確診新型肺炎，患者住在該座首名確診女子的相鄰單位。港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇下午聯同環境局副局長謝展寰，以及港大及科大專家，再到祿泉樓視察。袁國勇表示，新增個案病人，鼻咽及喉嚨的上呼吸道，並無發現病毒感染，但卻在肺部發現新型冠狀病毒，即是他好可能吸入了一些比飛沫還要細的微粒，令人懷疑空氣傳播有可能發生，因此有需要做測試，找出原因及可能的傳播途徑，但他呼籲居民，現階段不必擔心，亦不需要整座大廈疏散。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇解釋，一般感染新型冠狀病毒的人，整個呼吸道，由上到下都會感染，而通常的感染途徑是經飛沫傳播，而飛沫通常有5至10微米，因此很少會出現上呼吸道無病毒、而下呼吸道有病毒的情況，今次確診病人的情況顯示，他有可能吸入了一些細過5微米，甚至細過1微米的微粒。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又說，今日確診的患者，曾經兩次接受病毒測試，都無發現病毒，但卻表示有不適，醫生最後透過電腦素描，發現肺部有黑影，再以氣管鏡檢查才發現病毒。他說正與衞生署商討，是否對所有接受隔離的人士進行抽血驗血清，詳情仍在商討，呼籲大家不必心急。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531894-20200613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531894-20200613.htm&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJriQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=b0c38d59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531894-20200613.htm&h=14f45e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531894-20200613.htm</a>"},{"pid":"41a3f35f0e3d4ec2cea555cc1038447a4b6f9a87","tid":2062825,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"空氣微粒"},{"pid":"3a8ee2c54a985b0c02f010f24820016cb43d9307","tid":2062825,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d24227e68e2d4ad141f62a5367fd22e1aee388","tid":2062825,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"所以限聚令...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4330ebfedfd1c688fbfc195c75cbbda78568078","tid":2062825,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"搞到今日今日，<br />\n近幾次個爆發範圍都係差唔多定點，<br />\n有陣時會覺得係咪上面派人落黎放病毒，<br />\n話哂武漢實驗室出黎既"},{"pid":"b76dabefe10fb02d0e41ca9596fb3481f64c4ced","tid":2062825,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a8ee2c54a985b0c02f010f24820016cb43d9307","tid":2062825,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"的確係實驗室撚樣拎蝙蝠黎試毒，唔小心放左出去"},{"pid":"26bdcbdef8298f4bf0ba730e282e2a33c8e6366e","tid":2062825,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"豬嘴ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6c47388c5f1b97b771a743716422a419ccd658","tid":2062825,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"Encore<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09eb267d2baf431ee401ae432a5ea7d613707f5","tid":2062825,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和你「提」清MPF</span></span><br />\n爭取BNO平權<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200612/s00004/1591901008841/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200612%2Fs00004%2F1591901008841%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJriQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=4c7939a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200612%2Fs00004%2F1591901008841%2F&h=030d06fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://new